Former teammate of Kakashi Hatake and Rin Nohara, under Minato Namikaze
Was believed to have died during the Third Great Ninja War.
Was rescued and trained by Madara Uchiha.
Adopted the identity of "Tobi" and later "Madara Uchiha" to conceal himself
His worldview was shattered after witnessing Rin's death by Kakashi's hand


-Obito Uchiha
